1
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:34,979
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,770 --> 00:01:38,450
[2004]

3
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:40,840
Xiaolan.

4
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,280
The original host is very sick

5
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,310
and couldn't make it.

6
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,070
You stepped up in this crisis.

7
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:45,470
I am very grateful to you.

8
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:47,070
If you are really nervous,

9
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:47,509
just imagine the audience

10
00:01:47,509 --> 00:01:48,640
as big watermelons.

11
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,729
Xia Xiaolan.

12
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,870
Don't be nervous.

13
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,729
I will help you.

14
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:58,770
Come on.

15
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,040
Are you ready?

16
00:02:09,070 --> 00:02:12,190
[Episode 19]
[Step Onto My Stage]

17
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:15,280
May I ask, Ms. Wu Kaili,

18
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,120
how much are you paid

19
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,380
to be the brand ambassador for Elegance?

20
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,280
So is it 10,000 yuan on their side

21
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,030
and 100,000 yuan on ours?

22
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,190
Were these reporters' questions

23
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,650
not screened beforehand?

24
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:32,750
Let's go.

25
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,690
We've seen enough of the show.

26
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,030
Don't be so impatient. Please.

27
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,560
I'm so happy today

28
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,470
that I almost forgot—

29
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:39,280
I've prepared

30
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,190
lots of generous little gifts

31
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:41,560
backstage for everyone.

32
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,360
I hope you can go

33
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:42,870
and pick something you like.

34
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,520
We don't want gifts.

35
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,050
Alright?

36
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,120
Thank you. Thank you.

37
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:47,840
Thank you.

38
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,520
Explain yourself!

39
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,630
What's going on? Seriously.

40
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,310
Exactly.

41
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,360
Come on, let's have a drink.

42
00:02:59,360 --> 00:02:59,820
Cheers.

43
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,190
Thank you, San.

44
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:06,130
May you always have more than you need.

45
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:06,990
Thank you, San.

46
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,000
Are you...

47
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,750
Are you that movie star,

48
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,430
Teresa Li?

49
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,160
Yes, I am.

50
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,400
I'm your fan.

51
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:20,800
-I'm... May I...
-San.

52
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:21,520
Calm down.

53
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:22,930
Keep a low profile.

54
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:24,910
Alright, you guys enjoy your meal.

55
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,680
Just wave me over if you need anything.

56
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,010
Okay.

57
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:26,880
Thanks a lot.

58
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,140
Come on.

59
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:31,710
Look at this.

60
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:32,150
Xia.

61
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,360
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

62
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,090
Thanks to your brilliant plan,

63
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,240
otherwise, we wouldn't

64
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,770
have stolen the show today.

65
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,000
Now I understand what you said that day:

66
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,800
though Ji Ya was the one
who set the stage,

67
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,630
the performer

68
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,079
might not necessarily be her.

69
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,680
Now that you mentioned performing,

70
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,410
shouldn't you toast to Teresa?

71
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:49,400
Her acting skills

72
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,960
are truly masterful.

73
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,430
When the reporters were chasing her
with questions,

74
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,400
that aggrieved look

75
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,860
was performed perfectly.

76
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:57,520
It was all thanks to
your arrangement, Ms. Xia.

77
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,030
Ms. Xia.

78
00:03:58,310 --> 00:03:59,630
I think you'd make

79
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:00,750
a pretty good director someday.

80
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:01,560
When that happens,

81
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,750
I'll be your leading lady.

82
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,150
Okay.

83
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,800
Let's sign the contract now—

84
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,120
in case you become too famous later.

85
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,520
Zhou.

86
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,310
Alright, Ms. Xia.

87
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:10,310
I'll print the contract right away.

88
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,050
Cheers.

89
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,240
Eat up.

90
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,610
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

91
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:29,770
Mr. Chen,

92
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,490
thank you for today.

93
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,490
You're welcome.

94
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:33,740
You coming to shoot the commercial

95
00:04:33,740 --> 00:04:35,200
really helped me out a lot.

96
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,040
To be honest,

97
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,600
I didn't expect

98
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,800
you to agree so readily.

99
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,000
After all, you are...

100
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:42,250
An award-winning actress, you know.

101
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,360
Then I'll be honest with you too.

102
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,390
When I went on stage today

103
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,120
and heard the audience cheering,

104
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,630
I felt a little proud.

105
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,720
But when Wu Kaili went on stage

106
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,480
and I saw the audience's reaction,

107
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,360
I realized the gap

108
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,420
between myself and a real superstar.

109
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,600
After our commercial airs,

110
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,060
you'll be a superstar too.

111
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,120
Right.

112
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,090
I want to be a superstar too.

113
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:05,800
Well,

114
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,070
I'll be going now.

115
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,110
See you next time, Mr. Chen.

116
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:08,750
See you.

117
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,360
Sir,

118
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:15,190
please be careful on the road.

119
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:15,990
Drive safely.

120
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:29,510
Can't bear to see her go?

121
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,390
Why not take her to the station then?

122
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:32,680
It's true that I don't want her to leave.

123
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,240
But she's a famous actress,

124
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,830
and she'll be a superstar in the future.

125
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,950
Even if I can see her off
at the station today—

126
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,210
what about the future?

127
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,159
Forget it.

128
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:43,020
Let nature take its course.
I won't force it.

129
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,159
Oh, so you're not forcing it, huh?

130
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,120
I was thinking of

131
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,480
creating a chance for you.

132
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,340
Forget it then.

133
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:48,750
Let's go.

134
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:49,810
Alright, let's go.

135
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,880
What do you mean?

136
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,430
Are the school uniforms

137
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:54,560
for donation ready?

138
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,750
They're being loaded now

139
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,750
in Longcheng.

140
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,159
They'll arrive in 2 days.

141
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,120
Alright. When the time comes,

142
00:05:59,120 --> 00:05:59,800
go to the donation site

143
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,070
with Teresa.

144
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,560
I'm sure some reporters

145
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,430
will be willing to go with you guys.

146
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:06,190
Her workplace seems to have learned

147
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,650
about her donation today.

148
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,600
People are gossiping,

149
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:11,410
saying she acted on her own

150
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,010
without getting approval.

151
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:16,800
Even doing a good deed gets questioned?

152
00:06:17,890 --> 00:06:18,360
It's okay.

153
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,600
Comfort her first.

154
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,530
Once public opinion builds up,

155
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:22,430
a good reputation

156
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,760
will become her shield.

157
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,330
What about the commercial?

158
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:28,790
Just wait.

159
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:29,550
We're off.

160
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,060
See you.

161
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,630
What's with that reporter Mr. Liu?

162
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,600
Where's the big feature he promised?

163
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,190
I contacted Mr. Liu

164
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:41,680
as soon as I saw the newspaper.

165
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,270
He said

166
00:06:42,290 --> 00:06:44,630
he wrote the article
based on newsworthiness.

167
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:45,630
That Chen Xiliang

168
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,870
claims Teresa Li donated money
on one hand,

169
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,870
while saying it costs 100,000 yuan

170
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:49,800
to invite a Gangdao star on the other.

171
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,480
Isn't that clearly

172
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,480
targeting me?

173
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,120
Actors here

174
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:55,000
get paid very little for filming.

175
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,630
I don't believe

176
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,360
she'd be willing to donate 10,000 yuan

177
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,490
to buy uniforms for the students here.

178
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,240
Can we get a reporter

179
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,920
to interview that Teresa Li?

180
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,600
As long as we can confirm

181
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,260
her donation was fabricated.

182
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,530
If Teresa Li's

183
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,830
donation was fake,

184
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,870
then that guy surnamed Chen from Luna

185
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:13,270
is a fraud too.

186
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:15,830
Businessmen all just want to make money.

187
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:16,800
How could they bear

188
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,120
to give any of it away?

189
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,360
You might not know Xia Xiaolan

190
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,270
well enough.

191
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,890
I don't think

192
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,000
she would leave us

193
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,120
such leverage.

194
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,360
If we really take a reporter

195
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,560
to investigate Luna,

196
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:31,680
but Teresa Li

197
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,480
actually donated the uniforms,

198
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,600
wouldn't we just be giving free publicity

199
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,560
to Luna

200
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,920
and Teresa Li?

201
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,870
The most important thing right now

202
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:41,530
is to get the newspaper to stop

203
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,360
talking about Luna and Teresa Li

204
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:46,190
and instead
give our Elegance's fashion show

205
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,190
the upper hand.

206
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:48,909
By the way,

207
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,750
Teresa Li said

208
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:52,510
she filmed a commercial for Luna.

209
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,240
I wonder where

210
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,190
it will be aired.

211
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,970
Understood. I'll go investigate.

212
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,080
Granny Yu.

213
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:05,000
Do you think Xiaolan

214
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,240
can really get the advertisement

215
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,070
to be aired right after the news?

216
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,040
If Xiaolan says she can,
then she definitely can.

217
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,640
Let's have faith in Xiaolan.

218
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:40,840
Why don't you turn it on?

219
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,320
I don't care.

220
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:47,120
I don't believe

221
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,630
they can do it.

222
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,230
It's time.

223
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,790
It's on.

224
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,960
Welcome to Luna.

225
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,730
It's really airing!

226
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:21,720
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

227
00:09:22,950 --> 00:09:25,270
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

228
00:09:25,950 --> 00:09:28,240
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

229
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:35,650
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

230
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:34,670
Luna looks forward to welcoming you again.

231
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,440
Luna, Luna—a fashion legend.

232
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:39,060
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

233
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,750
Franchise Hotline...

234
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,440
Looks pretty decent.

235
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:42,830
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

236
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,000
0577-688888.

237
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,370
Luna Brand Promise:

238
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,670
for every item sold,

239
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:45,790
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

240
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,390
we donate 1 yuan.

241
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,030
That number is easy to remember.

242
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,300
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

243
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,150
688...

244
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,080
-888.
-888, symbolizing prosperity.

245
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:52,680
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

246
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:50,960
Xiaolan.

247
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,360
That commercial you shot was awesome.

248
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:57,810
♪ Our youth ♪

249
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:54,600
That kind of creativity—

250
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,440
I've never seen anything like it.

251
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,770
Of course it's awesome.

252
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,700
Let me tell you,

253
00:09:57,750 --> 00:09:58,840
when we were editing the shots,

254
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:01,670
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

255
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,750
even the director said
it was very imaginative.

256
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,670
He said that nowadays,

257
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,600
no one shoots commercials like this.

258
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:05,140
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

259
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,550
Actually, when we were filming,

260
00:10:04,550 --> 00:10:06,000
I didn't really like it.

261
00:10:05,350 --> 00:10:08,120
♪ We never give up ♪

262
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,150
But watching it now,
it's really something.

263
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:08,630
Ms. Xia,

264
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:12,110
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

265
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,440
you really should be a director.

266
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,240
I've just watched a lot.

267
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:15,290
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

268
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:13,630
Well,

269
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,600
have you all memorized the phone number?

270
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:18,670
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

271
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,560
Of course.

272
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,370
0577-6 followed by five 8s.

273
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,240
Zhenzhu?

274
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:21,780
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

275
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,030
0577-6 followed by five 8s.

276
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,870
Even I've memorized it!

277
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:25,370
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

278
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:25,480
0577-688888.

279
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:31,260
♪ That'd be enough ♪

280
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:27,790
Right. 0577-6...

281
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:30,030
Followed by prosperity and wealth!

282
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,150
This really worked out.

283
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:31,670
Chen,

284
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,870
just wait for the calls
to start coming in.

285
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,400
Alright.

286
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,150
This bowl is on me.

287
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:36,630
My idol.

288
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,030
When you came last time,

289
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,360
I didn't get a chance
to take a photo with you.

290
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:39,960
Today,

291
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,820
can I take a photo with you?

292
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:45,590
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

293
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:43,910
Of course.

294
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:44,840
Great.

295
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,000
Qiang!

296
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:49,060
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

297
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,630
Camera! Get the camera!

298
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:48,150
Alright. Coming.

299
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:48,670
Qiang!

300
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,030
Camera! Get the camera!

301
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:52,040
♪ We never give up ♪

302
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:50,650
Hurry up!

303
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:56,030
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

304
00:10:52,790 --> 00:10:53,550
Hurry up!

305
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:59,210
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

306
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:02,600
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

307
00:11:02,730 --> 00:11:05,640
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

308
00:11:06,130 --> 00:11:09,290
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

309
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:15,180
♪ That'd be enough ♪

310
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,790
It's really convenient to have a car.

311
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:22,670
This way, I can take you

312
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,030
directly to the station,

313
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,760
so you don't have to take a taxi.

314
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,560
This is Ms. Xia's car, right?

315
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:29,670
Yes, it is.

316
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,940
When Luna opens 20 stores,

317
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,030
I'll buy a car too.

318
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:35,240
Going out to negotiate business

319
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,480
will be more convenient,

320
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,510
and people will think more highly of me.

321
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:40,630
How many people do you think

322
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,560
saw our ad that aired today?

323
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,000
I usually don't switch channels

324
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,240
right after the news.

325
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,280
Don't worry.

326
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,510
A lot of people

327
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,630
must have seen it.

328
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:55,600
After today,

329
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,270
you'll be a superstar.

330
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,240
I heard that those stars

331
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,700
all have their own drivers
and private cars.

332
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,550
I won't get to drive you around
in the future.

333
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:09,840
Mr. Chen.

334
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:12,150
About the future,

335
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:15,520
don't jump to conclusions so quickly.

336
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,000
Mr. Chen.

337
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:24,870
Drive safely.

338
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:25,750
Okay.

339
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,330
The ad has aired.

340
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,150
Give it a few days to build momentum,

341
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,080
and franchisees

342
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:38,840
will be lining up

343
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,320
at Luna's door,

344
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,630
and Chen Xiliang will be

345
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,030
answering phone calls nonstop.

346
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:43,690
Zhou Cheng,

347
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:45,340
I'm just so happy!

348
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,150
You haven't been drinking today.

349
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,390
Why do you seem so tipsy?

350
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:52,670
Because achieving a dream

351
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,200
is intoxicating like that.

352
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,320
Once Luna has

353
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,380
over 50 franchisees,

354
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:58,190
I'll pull out.

355
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,150
Then I'll draw my own blueprints

356
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,350
and do my own designs.

357
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,890
I want to build the best houses

358
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:04,090
in all of Shengcheng!

359
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,240
I want to be a real estate developer!

360
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,550
I want to be a designer!

361
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:10,810
Zhou Cheng.

362
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:12,480
Do you think this dream of mine

363
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,600
is too big?

364
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,080
Do you think I'm talking big?

365
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,870
The Xia Xiaolan I know

366
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,540
has always dared to dream.

367
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,420
Back when she had nothing,

368
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:26,710
she was already dreaming of
conquering the world.

369
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:27,600
And now,

370
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,200
she has carved out

371
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,840
a world of her own.

372
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,490
Xiaolan,

373
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:36,640
dream to your heart's content.

374
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,840
You deserve

375
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,840
a broader future.

376
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,210
No matter what you become,

377
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,300
I'll be there by your side.

378
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,960
One million?

379
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,150
Where did you get that much money?

380
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:58,080
Besides, we're a clothing brand.

381
00:13:58,330 --> 00:14:00,360
How did you convince Hua TV?

382
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,630
Ms. Liu,

383
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,600
just get ready

384
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,890
for Luna's expansion.

385
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,240
In this era,

386
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,750
as long as you dare to dream,

387
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,080
nothing is impossible.

388
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:10,680
Alright.

389
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:13,910
Why did Granny Yu

390
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:15,240
go to bed so early today?

391
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:17,720
She might be tired from the day.

392
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,840
After watching the ad,

393
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,780
she went back to her room.

394
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:21,440
She's probably asleep by now.

395
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:24,840
Then let's celebrate quietly.

396
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:26,360
Here.

397
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:46,680
Where did I go with Mom and Dad that year?

398
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:49,170
Why is it that I still can't remember?

399
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,550
Before I knew it,

400
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:27,220
you've been with me for so long.

401
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:30,180
Through every important moment,

402
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:32,510
success or disappointment,

403
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,620
you've been by my side.

404
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:39,030
Maybe I can tell you everything.

405
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:44,120
Wait, Xia Xiaolan, what are you thinking?

406
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,240
In this era,

407
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:45,870
how could anyone possibly believe in

408
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,730
something like transmigration?

409
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:58,200
But what if I give it a try?

410
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,550
What if...

411
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:04,790
Better not overthink it.

412
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:09,550
One yuan will be donated
for every item sold.

413
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:11,240
Can we really trust that donation?

414
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:12,320
[Luna]

415
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:13,840
I heard the uniforms Teresa Li donated

416
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,320
have already been sent to the school.

417
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,520
So how do they donate?

418
00:16:16,540 --> 00:16:17,600
They record every sale?

419
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,550
How would I know?

420
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:20,810
Someone's coming out.

421
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:24,240
First of all,

422
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,390
I'd like to thank you all

423
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,600
for your support of Luna.

424
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,480
I hope later

425
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,630
you can line up properly,

426
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:30,080
so you don't block traffic

427
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,080
or affect

428
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,240
other stores' business.

429
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,630
Thank you for your cooperation.

430
00:16:33,630 --> 00:16:34,390
Let's go. Let's go.

431
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,030
Quick, quick. Line up.

432
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,430
Line... Line... Line up.

433
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:38,200
Is it true that for every item sold,

434
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,080
you'll donate 1 yuan?

435
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,410
This isn't a scam, is it?

436
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:42,200
Luna has always operated with integrity.

437
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,240
We would absolutely never scam anyone.

438
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,370
Please come inside.

439
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:44,970
Let's go.

440
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,000
Steamed buns! Steamed buns!

441
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:47,960
Watch your step.

442
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:49,000
Thank you.

443
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:49,790
Thank you, everyone.

444
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:51,250
Hot steamed buns for sale!

445
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:51,730
Come on.

446
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,600
Watch... Watch your step.

447
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:56,120
[Office]

448
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:54,560
Mr. Zhang.

449
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,870
Right, right, right.

450
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,320
Yes.

451
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,870
Just follow the

452
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:00,750
address on the business card

453
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:01,670
and come on over.

454
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:03,200
Thanks for supporting Luna.

455
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,800
Alright. Goodbye. Goodbye.

456
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:09,880
Hello?

457
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,440
Mr. Li. Mr. Li.

458
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:11,829
No.

459
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:12,750
No, I mean...

460
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:13,400
Jiang... Mr. Jiang.

461
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,160
I know. I know.

462
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,089
Hold on a second.

463
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:16,200
Alright, alright.

464
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,800
You can come over. Of course.

465
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,550
Sorry about that, Mr. Jiang.

466
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:20,750
There's a limit on the amount.

467
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:21,950
Thank you. Thank you.

468
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,109
Mr. Chen.

469
00:17:23,109 --> 00:17:24,310
Come take the calls for a while.

470
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,160
Mr. Liu will be here in a second.

471
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:25,790
I'll go meet him.

472
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:26,450
Okay. Okay.

473
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,310
Hello. Hi.

474
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,270
This is

475
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:30,600
Luna Clothing Co., Ltd.

476
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:31,720
Chen Xiliang! Mr. Chen!

477
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:32,960
We want to join Luna!

478
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:35,550
I know, I know. I got it.

479
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,640
Thank you, everyone. Thank you, everyone.

480
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,640
Please be patient, everyone.

481
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,880
I'm the General Manager of Luna,

482
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:39,680
Chen Xiliang.

483
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,380
We'll arrange for someone

484
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:42,880
to speak with you one-on-one
in a minute,

485
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,310
all right?

486
00:17:42,890 --> 00:17:44,620
[Luna Clothing Group]

487
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,810
One moment, please.

488
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:45,970
Okay.

489
00:17:46,110 --> 00:17:46,550
Mr. Chen.

490
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:47,070
Mr. Liu.

491
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,160
Come, please come in.

492
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,550
Okay.

493
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:49,680
Luna will make arrangements for all of you

494
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,640
one by one.

495
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:51,960
Just a moment. Right away.

496
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:52,510
Mr. Chen,

497
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:53,880
tell me about it.

498
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,310
How did your idea

499
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,920
of donating 1 yuan

500
00:17:57,510 --> 00:17:59,400
for every item sold come about?

501
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:02,750
To be honest, I'm a bit embarrassed
to say this.

502
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:04,110
When I first started making some money

503
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:05,400
from clothing,

504
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,240
my first thought

505
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:08,610
was not about charity—

506
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:09,670
I actually

507
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:10,720
bought myself

508
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:12,160
a cell phone right away.

509
00:18:12,210 --> 00:18:13,210
A cell phone, huh?

510
00:18:13,470 --> 00:18:14,670
Later, I was inspired

511
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:16,170
by Ms. Teresa Li.

512
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,160
I thought, if she could

513
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:18,960
take her own acting fees

514
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,110
and donate them

515
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,310
without hesitation,

516
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,510
then why can't I

517
00:18:22,510 --> 00:18:24,070
use the money I earned

518
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,510
for charity too,

519
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,840
to help those in need?

520
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:31,720
So, Mr. Chen, regarding this promise,

521
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:33,790
when do you plan to start fulfilling it?

522
00:18:33,790 --> 00:18:35,350
And when will it end?

523
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:37,400
It starts today.

524
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:39,750
And every month from now on,

525
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:41,110
we will publicly announce

526
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:41,830
our

527
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:45,110
sales figures and donation amounts.

528
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:47,000
I also hope that you, Mr. Liu,

529
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,590
along with

530
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:48,800
our other friends from the media

531
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:49,620
and the TV station,

532
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:51,150
can supervise us together.

533
00:18:52,490 --> 00:18:54,170
And as for

534
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,860
when it will end, as you asked,

535
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,080
let me put it this way—

536
00:18:59,350 --> 00:18:59,960
unless

537
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,160
the brand Luna goes out of business.

538
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:03,830
And even if

539
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:05,290
Luna goes out of business,

540
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:07,000
our donations won't stop.

541
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:09,200
So, Mr. Chen,

542
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:11,760
could you please disclose

543
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:12,920
your brand's sales figures

544
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,650
for October?

545
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,640
Currently, in Shengcheng and Longcheng,

546
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,400
we have 7 stores.

547
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:20,440
The sales figures for last month are—

548
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:22,280
we sold a total of

549
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:24,790
5,765 items nationwide.

550
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:28,510
5,765 items?

551
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,830
So the monthly donation

552
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:32,150
is over 5,000 yuan.

553
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:34,510
And the amount of donation for a year

554
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:36,240
would be 60,000 or 70,000 yuan.

555
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:37,350
Mr. Chen,

556
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:39,480
can you take responsibility

557
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,680
for what you've said?

558
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:41,960
Of course I can.

559
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,920
Right now,

560
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,550
I'm not capable enough yet.

561
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:47,880
I'll keep working hard.

562
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,440
If the brand Luna

563
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:51,770
can continue to grow bigger and stronger,

564
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:54,030
the donation amount will also increase.

565
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:54,960
I look forward to

566
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:56,680
the day when we can donate 10,000 yuan,

567
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,340
50,000 yuan

568
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,040
or even 100,000 yuan a month.

569
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:00,790
Donate 100,000 yuan a month?

570
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:03,030
So for a year,

571
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:04,890
that would be over 1 million yuan.

572
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:06,440
Mr. Chen,

573
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:08,310
you really dare to dream.

574
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:10,640
Can I take a photo with you

575
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,440
as a souvenir?

576
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,000
Sure.

577
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:12,880
Alright.

578
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:21,170
[Sold Today]

579
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:23,080
That's 98 yuan for 2 items after discount.

580
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:24,960
-Here.
-Alright.

