00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:23,720
hate those

872
00:30:23,750 --> 00:30:25,720
treacherous betrayers the most.

873
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,270
Now that I know,

874
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,700
how could I let them go?

875
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:30,830
You two

876
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:32,440
offending Ms. Xia

877
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:34,330
equals offending me, Du Zhaohui.

878
00:30:35,820 --> 00:30:36,500
Mr. Du.

879
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,590
I'm worthless!

880
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:40,790
I only incited Kaili
to breach the contract

881
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:43,030
to make some more money.

882
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,200
Mr. Du.

883
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,160
Ms. Xia.

884
00:30:45,270 --> 00:30:45,960
I was wrong!

885
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,040
I was wrong.

886
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:47,550
You two,

887
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:48,790
please be the bigger person

888
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:50,030
and spare me!

889
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,720
In the past,

890
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,720
I would have handled this myself.

891
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,510
Now, I'm handing you two

892
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:56,960
over to Ms. Xia.

893
00:30:59,590 --> 00:31:01,160
This is my gift to you.

894
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,960
What are you doing?

895
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:06,420
Stop it!

896
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,000
Du Zhaohui.

897
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:12,330
Are you out of your mind?

898
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:14,320
What on earth are you thinking?

899
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,440
Thinking of making you happy, of course.

900
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,500
They betrayed you.

901
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,890
Don't you want to teach them a lesson?

902
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:21,650
To be honest,

903
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,920
seeing them like this,

904
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,270
doesn't it feel good?

905
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,550
It does.

906
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,550
It is pretty satisfying indeed.

907
00:31:28,550 --> 00:31:29,240
But I'm not the type to enjoy

908
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:31,170
watching people fight each other.

909
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,790
Yuefeng led Wu Kaili
to breach the contract.

910
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:35,440
I'll find a way to strike back

911
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:37,410
in business using legal means.

912
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,640
I just want to

913
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,750
run my business properly.

914
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:41,750
Why are you trying to hand me a knife?

915
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,170
Xia Xiaolan.

916
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:52,410
You are really hard to please.

917
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,510
You are tolerant of others

918
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,550
but picky with me.

919
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,030
Are you taking advantage of the fact
that I like you

920
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:59,060
to bully me?

921
00:32:01,510 --> 00:32:03,000
Who's bullying whom here?

922
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:04,640
Du Zhaohui.

923
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:07,000
I appreciate your help,

924
00:32:07,640 --> 00:32:09,160
but our styles of handling things

925
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,640
are completely different.

926
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:11,300
Let them go.

927
00:32:14,830 --> 00:32:16,000
Ms. Xia and Mr. Du

928
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,720
are not on the same side.

929
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:18,980
We still have a chance.

930
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:21,090
Ms. Xia, I'm sorry.

931
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,590
I broke the rules.

932
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,020
Please forgive me.

933
00:32:24,210 --> 00:32:25,170
I won't take

934
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:26,380
Elegance's commercials anymore.

935
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:27,400
If Ji Ya wants me to pay damages,

936
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,400
I... I'll pay.

937
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:29,510
Right.

938
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,200
Take whatever commercials you want—

939
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,600
it's none of my business.

940
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,050
But I'm telling you,

941
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:37,000
if you keep acting like this,

942
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,240
your image will easily collapse,

943
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:40,770
and your reputation will be ruined
in no time.

944
00:32:40,790 --> 00:32:41,350
Ms. Xia.

945
00:32:41,590 --> 00:32:42,920
Please be magnanimous.

946
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,620
You're bound to achieve great success.

947
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:45,350
Your brand

948
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:46,590
will surely become popular nationwide,

949
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,590
even worldwide!

950
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:49,730
I don't want to see them again.

951
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:51,900
Get out!

952
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,030
All of you, get out!

953
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:54,490
Come on.

954
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,000
Fish him out.

955
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:00,750
Hurry up and go.

956
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,680
That way.

957
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:02,350
Move.

958
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:05,500
It's getting late.

959
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,760
I should head back too.

960
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,310
Wait.

961
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:09,930
I want to ask you,

962
00:33:10,830 --> 00:33:11,480
is it that no matter

963
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,350
what I do,

964
00:33:13,070 --> 00:33:14,670
you will never be satisfied?

965
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,110
You helped me,

966
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,480
and I thanked you.

967
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,110
It's nothing against you.

968
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:20,680
It's just...

969
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:21,920
It's just that you won't like me.

970
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:22,350
Yes.

971
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:25,550
There's no point in lying to you.

972
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:26,510
Du Zhaohui.

973
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:28,310
I've already found someone I like.

974
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:29,010
As for you,

975
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:30,640
you can get whatever kind of woman

976
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,440
you want.

977
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:32,640
There's no need to

978
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:33,570
waste time on me.

979
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:34,560
I'm leaving.

980
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:38,060
What do you like about that Jerk Zhou?

981
00:33:40,070 --> 00:33:40,960
His name is Zhou Cheng.

982
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:41,510
I know.

983
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:42,690
I hate his name.

984
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,000
He's nothing but

985
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,000
a small-time attorney.

986
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:47,310
He's only slightly more handsome than me.

987
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:47,970
Does he have money?

988
00:33:47,970 --> 00:33:48,590
Is he famous?

989
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:49,510
Does he have connections?

990
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,970
In what way can he help you?

991
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,460
He can give me respect.

992
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,570
Respect from a pauper?

993
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,880
Do you know how Zhou Cheng and I

994
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:58,880
met each other?

995
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,110
Back then,

996
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,480
I was just a poor,

997
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:03,790
disgraced

998
00:34:03,790 --> 00:34:04,750
village girl,

999
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:07,680
while he was from the Jingcheng compounds.

1000
00:34:08,070 --> 00:34:08,920
He was smart

1001
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,000
and savvy.

1002
00:34:10,510 --> 00:34:11,190
In one summer,

1003
00:34:11,190 --> 00:34:12,989
he could earn tens of thousands.

1004
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:15,070
As long as he wants to make money,

1005
00:34:15,070 --> 00:34:15,840
whether in Jingcheng

1006
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:16,699
or Shengcheng,

1007
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:18,110
he will have a place.

1008
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:22,070
They say
beauty is in the eye of the beholder.

1009
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:24,440
But for you, it's a cash cow you see,
isn't it?

1010
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:24,920
Whether I'm

1011
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,580
Xia Xiaolan from Dahe Village

1012
00:34:26,650 --> 00:34:27,360
or Xia Xiaolan who graduated from Huaqing

1013
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,510
and works at Luna,

1014
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:30,110
Zhou Cheng's love for me

1015
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:31,030
never changes.

1016
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:33,639
He likes me for who I am right now.

1017
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,560
No matter what I become,

1018
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:36,800
he will support me.

1019
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,760
I like you, too.

1020
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,820
I support you, too.

1021
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,710
I'm richer and more generous than him.

1022
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:45,510
I can give you even better things.

1023
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:45,920
Right.

1024
00:34:46,780 --> 00:34:47,400
You can give me

1025
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,840
more and better things.

1026
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:50,320
But you just

1027
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,760
want to use those things

1028
00:34:52,190 --> 00:34:53,110
to mold me into

1029
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:54,770
the Xia Xiaolan that you like.

1030
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,630
Zhou Cheng has never

1031
00:34:57,630 --> 00:34:59,230
asked me to change anything.

1032
00:34:59,510 --> 00:35:00,910
This is his respect for me

1033
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:01,880
and for

1034
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,320
our relationship,

1035
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:04,710
and I want to love him

1036
00:35:04,710 --> 00:35:06,070
with the same respect.

1037
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,000
Du Zhaohui.

1038
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:11,720
You probably don't understand.

1039
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:13,480
But precisely because you don't,

1040
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,480
there is even less of a chance

1041
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:15,360
for us.

1042
00:35:16,710 --> 00:35:17,310
Pardon me.

1043
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,150
I have to go.

1044
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:43,230
It's so big,

1045
00:35:43,230 --> 00:35:43,880
Xiaolan.

1046
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,760
I rented

1047
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,760
this whole floor.

1048
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:47,920
The rooms outside

1049
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,800
can be used as Yuanhui's office.

1050
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:51,800
Yuanhui is in charge of
Luna's interior design.

1051
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:54,150
And with so many prospective partners
coming by,

1052
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:54,960
it's high time we had

1053
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,000
a decent office.

1054
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,550
This is great.

1055
00:35:58,670 --> 00:35:59,670
You're spurring me on

1056
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,880
to run Yuanhui well

1057
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:02,070
and take on more quality projects.

1058
00:36:02,070 --> 00:36:03,110
Otherwise, I'd be letting down

1059
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:04,630
such a great office space.

1060
00:36:05,330 --> 00:36:06,930
I'm also spurring myself on.

1061
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:09,400
Luna has 27 stores now.

1062
00:36:09,710 --> 00:36:11,110
Once the store number reaches 50,

1063
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:13,240
I'll withdraw from daily operations.

1064
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:15,280
As Shengcheng develops faster and faster,

1065
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,630
if I don't speed up,

1066
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:17,840
I'll be left behind sooner or later.

1067
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,510
You want to open yet another company?

1068
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:20,440
Is Yuanhui still not enough?

1069
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,440
Our business

1070
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,480
will only expand further.

1071
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:23,760
So I think Yuanhui

1072
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,560
should still focus on

1073
00:36:25,590 --> 00:36:27,110
decoration and renovation,

1074
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:28,360
striving to become

1075
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,800
a leader in the industry.

1076
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:31,670
What I want to register

1077
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:33,070
is a real estate company.

1078
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:35,360
You want to buy land and build houses?

1079
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:35,800
Yes.

1080
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:38,280
But it won't be easy.

1081
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:39,760
As for funding, qualifications and stuff,

1082
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,360
I have to take it step by step.

1083
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,590
Anyway,

1084
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:44,310
this place

1085
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:45,880
will be where

1086
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,360
my dream sets sail.

1087
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:50,380
This is where my dream sets sail, too.

1088
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,890
Why don't I see Ge Jian?

1089
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:56,360
I lent Ge Jian and the car

1090
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,360
to Zhenzhu and Wei.

1091
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,360
They are going to

1092
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,840
the lighting fixture factory
to discuss cooperation today.

1093
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,710
I thought having a car

1094
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:01,550
would give them more face.

1095
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,800
You're such a thoughtful boss,

1096
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:03,590
even lending your car.

1097
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,510
You're really something.

1098
00:37:04,510 --> 00:37:06,630
I have shares in the materials center too,
after all.

1099
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:06,960
Yeah.

1100
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:07,480
Come on, Uncle.

1101
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:08,190
Let's go look around some more.

1102
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:08,590
Okay.

1103
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:12,030
This place is really great.

1104
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,280
What do you think,

1105
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:14,590
Uncle?

1106
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:15,960
It's really nice. Really nice.

1107
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,400
Every room is wonderful.

1108
00:37:19,510 --> 00:37:20,190
Zhou Cheng?

1109
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:21,690
Uncle, Xiaolan.

1110
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:22,920
How do you like this place?

1111
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,900
You're really something, kid.

1112
00:37:23,900 --> 00:37:25,880
You even managed to find this place.

1113
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:26,960
Riding that bike of yours

1114
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,560
to pick up our Xiaolan again?

1115
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:30,800
Can't you just buy a car?

1116
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:32,360
Didn't we make quite a lot of money

1117
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:34,000
reselling cigarettes back then?

1118
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:34,520
Uncle,

1119
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:35,680
I have all his money.

1120
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:37,960
Alright.

1121
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:38,760
You two go ahead and leave.

1122
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,550
I'll look around a bit longer.

1123
00:37:39,550 --> 00:37:39,860
Okay.

1124
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:40,710
Okay, we're leaving then.

1125
00:37:40,710 --> 00:37:41,280
We're off then.

1126
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:41,590
Okay.

1127
00:37:41,590 --> 00:37:42,520
Bye-bye, Uncle.

1128
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:51,000
I was thinking about
when we first came to Shengcheng—

1129
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:53,150
that time when Sis Bai and Wei

1130
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:55,080
were almost scammed by smugglers.

1131
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:56,190
The four of us

1132
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:58,070
were also sitting right here,

1133
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:58,800
drinking beers

1134
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,130
and eating roast goose.

1135
00:38:00,230 --> 00:38:01,490
It's only been 2 years,

1136
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:04,930
and you're already
reminiscing about the past, Ms. Xia?

1137
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,740
It's already been 2 years.

1138
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:10,070
Time really flies.

1139
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:13,920
It feels even longer than
the entire lifetime I had.

1140
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:14,510
So many things

1141
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:16,110
I never even dared to imagine

1142
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,320
have actually

1143
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:18,800
come true.

1144
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:23,130
You're saying strange things again.

1145
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:24,590
The Xia Xiaolan I know

1146
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:27,030
has already had great ambitions

1147
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,440
since her days in Dahe Village.

1148
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:28,920
What's there

1149
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:31,120
that even you wouldn't dare to dream of?

1150
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,720
Even those with great ambitions

1151
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:35,280
can be afraid sometimes—

1152
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:38,960
sometimes afraid of
not achieving their dreams,

1153
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,590
other times

1154
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:42,420
afraid of running too fast

1155
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:45,030
and having it all come to nothing.

